title: Door Kickers v2.0.0.1 Retail - CORE
description:
This is the latest, complete, retail, non-alpha non-beta version of Door Kickers, an awesome looking Breach & Clear clone.  

While the official RLSLOG statement says v1.0.0.2, the nfo and the filename say v2.0.0.1.  

Description:
Door Kickers, by  KillHouse Games, is an innovative realtime strategy game that puts you in charge of a SWAT team and lets you command them during a tactical intervention.

Features:
2D, Top Down for optimal tactical analysis
Real Time With Free Pause
No turns, no hexes, no action points or awkward interfaces
Realistic but action packed
Non-linear levels, freeform gameplay
Mission editor and modability
Unlimited gameplay via mission generator and level editor
Single Player (but MP might come later)
